The Supplier shall supply per dock leveller the following accessories:

- Control unit: {{ctrlType}}
- Bumpers: {{bumperType}}, quantity per leveller: {{bumperQty}}
- Weather seals: included as standard

All accessories shall be compatible with the supplied dock leveller model. The Supplier shall confirm compatibility and state any accessories not included in the base price.

STM reserves the right to reject non-compliant alternatives.
